        @Nullable
protected IndexCandidate createIndexCandidate(IndexType index,
                                                        MultiCondition<JanusGraphElement> conditions,
                                                        IndexSerializer serializer)
        Creates an IndexCandidate from a MultiCondition which it covers.
        Parameters:
        index -
        conditions - For the condition to be valid, it needs to match these rules:
        • It must be an equality condition
        • It must not cover multiple labels
        • The label must match the given index
        Returns:
        An instance of IndexCandidate if the parameter conditions is valid, null else.
